Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的報告沒有錯吧!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.48,0:00:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.95,0:00:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希的ANGEL  HEART
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.52,0:00:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經正常起動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.46,0:00:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解封ANGEL  HEART
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.49,0:00:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經有兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.13,0:00:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美果然是「改」的鑰匙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是「改」的起動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.23,0:00:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該需要咒術師的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.00,0:00:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，我們不可以坐視不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.81,0:00:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要盡快回收久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.20,0:02:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在別墅找回兩個好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.68,0:02:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵天使心臟的結構物質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.05,0:02:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有新鋼鐵天使的設計圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.02,0:02:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有都被人拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.79,0:02:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭度是敵國的間諜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還需要調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.36,0:02:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據情報局的報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潛伏在本國的間諜名單中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.33,0:03:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有像布蘭度般的人物在內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.14,0:03:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.94,0:03:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我國有新敵人在暗中活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.84,0:03:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要盡快處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.81,0:03:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以   為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.18,0:03:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若這些資料被人利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會對我們有很大影響的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是帝國陸軍部...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...是本國的危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵士兵計劃時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.86,0:03:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有軍隊內少數高層人士知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.93,0:03:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在國家北面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.47,0:03:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正需要大量人力物力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.87,0:03:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是說，對於未能確定的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.21,0:03:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊不能胡亂行動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若不能得到國家的批准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.34,0:03:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有權力命令行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.38,0:03:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...   妳閉咀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.95,0:03:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歸根究底是妳令這種事情發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.99,0:04:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城禮子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.70,0:04:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在X令妳退役，離開軍隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.07,0:04:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即日生效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將軍，請你解釋清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉唆!軍令如山，不用解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍人有很多不方便的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.89,0:04:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該有自由做些個人私務吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若我離開軍隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.86,0:04:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便可以單獨調查也不會連累軍隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.93,0:04:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個方法的確是更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.02,0:04:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我喜歡的一類...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小沙希，開始唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.26,0:05:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.97,0:05:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頗好玩唷   對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.97,0:05:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你們了，謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，說到底也是我弄毀你的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我應該做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.15,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我建的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.85,0:05:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的屋子唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會說謊唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小沙希很厲害唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.86,0:05:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這屋子我是為姐姐而建的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.50,0:05:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了我!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，是為姐姐而建的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.47,0:05:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?很感激妳唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳為了令久留美和主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可過夫婦生活而建的屋子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹太好了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐這麼開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的玫瑰，白色的窗台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊有姐姐在我身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.13,0:06:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想告訴姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人嚮往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們二人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也試試令人嚮往的生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.38,0:06:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城博士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.39,0:06:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到事情變成這樣，十分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.46,0:06:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，希望你可以告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.46,0:06:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼你會協助綾小路博士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣息?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.17,0:06:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由綾小路博士製造出來的她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.94,0:07:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感到一般新的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.71,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在綾小路博士的科學中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.08,0:07:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他加入了從遠古開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直保祐我們的咒術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科學與咒術?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信若她們真的可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,融合兩者的長處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後咒術和科學可以互補長短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的社會一定可以有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更大的進步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神人先生，我有一個請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.39,0:07:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡變成我們二人的愛巢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.17,0:08:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我用心佈置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.37,0:08:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也為了姐姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.91,0:08:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用心寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.01,0:08:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事?主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.62,0:08:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是，本來現在我應該
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.55,0:08:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和綾小路博士去出雲的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.39,0:08:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是世事難料呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美只要和主人一起便開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，我也是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去找尋綾小路博士的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.87,0:08:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有很多事要去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此，我們要趕快行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.98,0:08:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美和沙希的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.71,0:08:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有綾小路博士為甚麼被擄走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若我們去博士在出雲的研究室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該會找到一些線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和天城博士一起去出雲吧，仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.63,0:09:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和主人的愛巢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐好可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.84,0:09:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也...好可憐   主人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們明天要開始愛的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉祥寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.46,0:09:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小金井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.06,0:09:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們入來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.57,0:09:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始行動了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.18,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，好像準備出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.74,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目的地，出雲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們去暗中跟蹤他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若他們遇到危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暗中保護他們   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.95,0:11:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城博士，舍弟就麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓他安全回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.56,0:11:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人，你身負重任啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.90,0:11:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你這段時間的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人的事包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.67,0:12:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.64,0:12:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.88,0:12:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BYE  BI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.88,0:12:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜所占的凶卦真叫我擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.16,0:12:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人有科學和咒術的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守護天使跟隨著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，想深一層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在倒不錯唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.53,0:12:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，提起精神，一起出發唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「愛姊妹」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.34,0:14:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，這裡不行唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.07,0:14:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚麼也沒做過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.64,0:14:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是小沙希做的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我，姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.48,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是誰?撫摸久留美的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵天使久留美，第七話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.78,0:14:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「這裡不行唷!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不容錯過...唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.85,0:14:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，這裡不行唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚麼也沒做過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.19,0:14:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...是天城博士嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡說!怎可能是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.86,0:14:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是小沙希嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...我雖然很想...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.97,0:14:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不是我，姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撫摸久留美的那個地方
