Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子不用理會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.17,0:14:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵天使久留美，第七話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「這裡不行唷!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.71,0:14:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不容錯過...唷
