Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.05,0:15:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別太近看電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.09,0:15:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看下去便會知道
